<h3 id="responsive-variants">Responsive Variants</h3>
<p>Use responsive prefixes to apply different margins at different
breakpoints.</p>
<pre class="html"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;m-2 m-md-4 m-lg-6&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
